Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从矢量乘标量开始。\NWe begin with multiplication of a vector by a scalar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当你乘向量a时\NWhen you multiply a vector a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,通过标量，这个乘法因子只是重新缩放向量的大小或长度。\Nby a scalar, this multiplicative factor just re scales the magnitude or the length of the vector.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看向量两次\NLet us look at the vector two times a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这与向量a的方向相同，但长度是向量a的两倍。\Nthis is in the same direction as the vector a but is twice as long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是向量b\NThis is vector b
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,矢量由其大小和方向来定义。所以这个向量b在空间的任何地方都是一样的，包括在原点。\Na vector is defined by its magnitude and direction. So this vector b is the same anywhere in space, including at the origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我要负点乘以5，这个向量是b的反方向，是长度的一半。\NIf I want minus point five times be, this vector is in the opposite direction of b and is half the length.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在让我们看看向量加法。\NNow let's look at vector addition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是向量a，这里是b，我们如何用图形方式添加它们？\NHere's a vector a here is b how do we add them graphically?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把b的尾巴滑到a的头上\NWe slide the tail of b to the head of a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的和是从a的尾部到b的头部的向量\Nand their sum is the vector drawn from the tail of a to the head of b
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也可以把a的尾部滑动到b的头部来增加a到b\NI could have also added a to b by sliding the tail of a to the head of b
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以看到这是一个平行四边形，一些向量c\Nyou can see that this makes a parallelogram, and the some vector c
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,只是这个平行四边形的对角线。\Nis just the diagonal of this parallelogram.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是 啊。\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,减法可以看作是乘法和加法。\NSubtraction can be thought of as just multiplication and addition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果c等于a减去b\NIf I have c is equal to a minus b
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要把a加到向量减去b\NI just need to add a to the vector minus b
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,负b是负的1乘以b\Nminus b is negative one times b
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是向量。\Nwhich is this vector here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我只需要把a加到-b\NNow I only have to add a to minus b
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,再举一个例子\Nlet's do another example
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里。我的向量a和b不是从原点开始的。但是由于矢量在空间的任何地方都是一样的，我可以在这里进行这个过程。\Nhere. My vectors a and b do not start at the origin. But since vectors are the same anywhere in space, I can go through the process here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要a减b\NI want a minus b
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:02:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我先乘以我的负1，得到负b\Nso I first multiply be my minus one to find minus b
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我移动了负β的尾部\Nand then I moved the tail of minus beta, the head of a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,把这两个加起来。\Nand add the two like this.
